com.skyisland.questmanager.quest.requirements

Class PositionRequirement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.skyisland.questmanager.quest.requirements.Requirement
      • com.skyisland.questmanager.quest.requirements.PositionRequirement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompassTrackable, org.bukkit.event.Listener

    public class PositionRequirement
extends Requirement
implements org.bukkit.event.Listener, CompassTrackable
    Requirement that a participant must be at the provided location. Unlike the ArriveRequirement this requirement is that someone be located there for this to be completed. That means if they leave, the requirement will no longer be satisfied!
    See Also:
    ArriveRequirement
